  <bodyText><![CDATA[<div class="white_box_shadow">
<p><span class="geolocation-title"><img style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="/media/13071702/inghams-insiders-guide-best-value-ski-resorts-02.jpg" alt="Best Value Ski Resorts | Inghams Insider Guide's" data-udi="umb://media/eea5a042ad02475899ed5e77ab54ab27" /></span></p>
<p><span class="geolocation-title">Skiing and snowboarding isn't the cheapest hobby. Once lift passes and extravagant mountain lunches and après drinks have been tallied, how many of you are surprised by how much you’ve spent? But there are budget friendly ski resorts out there, and there are many ski destinations where the price of a beer doesn’t break the bank.</span></p>
<p>As an expert ski tour operator, Inghams knows where to find the best value ski resorts. So budget-seeking skiers and snowboarders <em>can</em> still afford to have fun when the winter draws in!</p>
<p>Plus, Inghams’ new <a data-udi="umb://document/3566891a2b9142d4afe57ea30f084428" href="/{localLink:umb://document/3566891a2b9142d4afe57ea30f084428}" title="Ski Inclusive Bundles"><strong>Ski Inclusive Bundles</strong></a> mean guests can benefit from big savings when they pre-book their lift passes, ski / board and boot hire.</p>
<div class="data-grid" style="float: center;">
